00:00:57.426 --> 00:00:59.300
And operator expressions,
because it lets you

00:00:59.300 --> 00:01:01.940
treat systems like polynomials.

00:01:01.940 --> 00:01:05.450
What we'll see today is that
that same kind of strategy

00:01:05.450 --> 00:01:06.980
