differential equations.

00:02:09.334 --> 00:02:11.000
And what we're going
to do is skip ahead

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:15.650
and think about the alternative
representations instead.

00:02:15.650 --> 00:02:19.160
So just like in DT,
where we thought

00:02:19.160 --> 00:02:21.400
about block diagrams,
which gave us

00:02:21.400 --> 00:02:23.360
a way of thinking about
signal flow paths,

00:02:23.360 --> 00:02:25.305
