similarly change.

00:03:23.180 --> 00:03:24.620
So the new operator,
the operator

00:03:24.620 --> 00:03:26.830
that we use to
represent a CT system,

00:03:26.830 --> 00:03:33.260
we'll call the A operator, A is
intended to mean accumulator.

00:03:33.260 --> 00:03:37.130
The thing that's in my mind
